OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FManchester City have declined to
OL,7,Fcomment on fresh reports claiming that
OL,8,Fmanager Pep Guardiola is set to stand
OL,9,Fdown at the end of the season.
OL,11,FReports claim that Sunday's final
OL,12,FPremier League fixture against Aston
OL,13,FVilla will be the Spaniard's last
OL,14,Fmatch in charge, bringing an end to
OL,15,Fhis 10 years at the helm.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
