OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FDespite the persistent speculation
OL,7,Fsurrounding the 55-year-old's future,
OL,8,FGuardiola still has one year remaining
OL,9,Fon his current contract. Manchester
OL,10,FCity's position on the matter has
OL,11,Fremained unchanged throughout the
OL,12,Fseason.
OL,14,FIt has been widely reported that
OL,15,Fformer Chelsea boss Enzo Maresca will
OL,16,Ftake over at the Etihad Stadium.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
