CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779207074
OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FThe 46-year-old, who was an assistant
OL,7,Fto Guardiola during City's treble-
OL,8,Fwinning campaign in 2022-23, has been
OL,9,Fout of work since leaving Stamford
OL,10,FBridge in January.
OL,12,FHis departure from Chelsea came after
OL,13,Fhe informed the club he had been in
OL,14,Fcontact on multiple occasions with
OL,15,FManchester City about taking over from
OL,16,FGuardiola.
OL,18,FGuardiola has overseen one of the most
OL,19,Fsuccessful managerial reigns in
OL,20,FEnglish football history.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
