PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779207074
OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FSince his appointment in 2016, City
OL,7,Fhave won 20 trophies including six
OL,8,FPremier League titles and the
OL,9,FChampions League.
OL,11,FThey have also won the FA Cup three
OL,12,Ftimes and lifted the Carabao Cup on
OL,13,Ffive occasions, including both
OL,14,Fcompetitions this season.
OL,16,FThey remain in contention for the
OL,17,FPremier League title and face
OL,18,FBournemouth on Tuesday, hoping to take
OL,19,Fthe race with Arsenal to the final
OL,20,Fweekend.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
