PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1779207074
OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FGuardiola gave mixed messages when
OL,7,Fasked about his future earlier on
OL,8,FMonday.
OL,10,FAt a press conference to preview
OL,11,FTuesday's trip to Bournemouth,
OL,12,FGuardiola referenced both the "one
OL,13,Fmore year" on his contract and a
OL,14,Fhypothetical new three-year deal.
OL,16,FYet, as he has on several occasions,
OL,17,Fhe stopped short of explicitly stating
OL,18,Fhe would remain at City next term.
