OL,3,CManchester City silent on reports of
OL,4,CPep Guardiola's departure
OL,6,FAfter being asked about Andoni
OL,7,FIraola's imminent departure from
OL,8,FBournemouth, Guardiola was questioned
OL,9,Fon whether he had thought about his
OL,10,Fown farewell.
OL,12,FHe sighed heavily and said: "Next
OL,13,F(question). So many times ` I have one
OL,14,Fmore year!"
